        <category name="Krieg Buzzaxe">
            <comment>Krieg's melee weapon needs its own flag.</comment>
            <code profiles="default">set GD_Lilac_SkillsBase.Buzzaxe.WeaponType_Buzzaxe bUsesPlayerLevelRequirement False</code>
        </category>

        <category name="Weapons (General Manufacturers)">
            <comment>Weapons are the hardest to enumerate because every manufacturer+type combination</comment>
            <comment>is a separate object definition. The FULL mod lists 1000+ weapon lines.</comment>
            <comment></comment>
            <comment>For weapons, the MOST RELIABLE approach is the Python SDK mod (see mods/ dir),</comment>
            <comment>which hooks the equip check at runtime and covers ALL weapons automatically.</comment>
            <comment></comment>
            <comment>Or download the complete NoLevelRequirement mod from Nexus Mods #94.</comment>
            <comment></comment>
            <comment>Below are a few common unique weapons as examples:</comment>
            <code profiles="default">set GD_Weap_Pistol.A_Weapons_Unique.Pistol_Bandit_3_Dahlminator bUsesPlayerLevelRequirement False</code>
